&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://justinhileman.info/&#34;&gt;Justin Hileman&lt;/a&gt; and I gave a presentation
on “Augmenting RDBMS with NoSQL for e-commerce” at the PgEast 2011
conference. This presentation is really the sequel (no pun intended) to
my presentation, &lt;a href=&#34;http://spf13.com/post/mongodb-ecommerce-a-perfect-combination&#34; title=&#34;MongoDB &amp;amp; Ecommerce : A Perfect Combination&#34;&gt;MongoDB &amp;amp; Ecommerce : A Perfect
Combination&lt;/a&gt;.
This presentation takes you through how we created a hybrid solution
blending both sql and nosql to achieve an optimal solution.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.slideshare.net/spf13/augmenting-rdbms-with-mongodb-for-ecommerce-7561455&#34; title=&#34;Augmenting RDBMS with MongoDB for ecommerce&#34;&gt;Augmenting RDBMS with MongoDB for
ecommerce&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
