&lt;p&gt;View more &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.slideshare.net/&#34;&gt;presentations&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.slideshare.net/spf13&#34;&gt;Steve
Francia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our colleague at &lt;a href=&#34;http://opensky.com&#34;&gt;OpenSky&lt;/a&gt;, Jon Wage, pioneered this
technique. To learn more about creating cross-database-platform
relations with Doctrine ORM and ODM, check out &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.jwage.com/2010/08/25/blending-the-doctrine-orm-and-mongodb-odm/&#34;&gt;Jon Wage’s excellent
blog post on the
subject&lt;/a&gt;
or the first half &lt;a href=&#34;http://symfony.com/video/Paris2011/575&#34;&gt;his recent talk at Symfony
